<!-- Using the form section -->
<h3 id="using-the-sitescout-form">Using the SiteScout Form</h3>
<p>Use the SiteScout form to update your FishTales starter file by importing two Excel files.</p>

<!-- Inputs section -->
<h5 id="inputs">Inputs</h5>
<ul>
    <li><strong>ShopReel File:</strong> Import the results file you got from ShopReel.</li>
    <li>
        <strong>FishTales Starter File:</strong> Import your current starter file, or use the
        <a href="/example_files/fishTales_starter_file.xlsx" download><strong>example file</strong></a>.
    </li>
</ul>
