</div>
<p>After selecting the files, click <strong>Compare</strong>. You‚Äôll see progress updates as SiteScout runs.</p>

<!-- Output files section -->
<h5 id="output-files">Output Files</h5>
<p class="mb-0">
    After running the comparison, SiteScout creates the following file:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>new_fishTales_starter.xlsx:</strong>
        Includes all the original entries plus any new sites found in your ShopReel results.<br>
        <em>Note:</em> Only new URLs are added; the rest of your file stays the same.
